		<item>
			<title>Andy Robertson</title>
			<link>https://nightland.website/index.php/about/authors-and-artists/107-andy-robertson</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">https://nightland.website/index.php/about/authors-and-artists/107-andy-robertson</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<p class="webmaster-note">The late Mr. Robertson founded this website in 2001. Aside from editing the site, he wrote stories developing the Night Land, and essays explicating it. Alas, he died in 2014.</p>
<h4>Stories:</h4>
<ul class="works-list">
<li><a href="https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/42-eater-part-1">Eater</a></li>
<li><a href="https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-days-of-darkening/97-delight-part-1">Delight</a></li>
