<h4>Poetry and Vignettes</h4>
<ul class="works-list">
<li><a href="https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/poetry/63-the-door-in-the-wall">The Door in the Wall</a></li>
<li><a href="https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/poetry/58-dream">Dream</a></li>
